dmca.title: Earthpulse.net Wants Alleged Infringer Out of Google
dmca.body:
Google, Inc
Attn: Customer Support, DMCA Complaints
[private]
Mountain View, CA 94043

RE: Copyright Infringement. 

Dear Google,

1) The copyrighted work at issue is the text that appears on my website at 
www.earthpulse.net and its subdirectories.

My name is [private]. I registered the web address www.earthpulse.net on 8/18/02 in my name, and have since researched, written and uploaded every keystroke on that website 
since its inception. It has been work in progress since */18/02

My trademark EarthPulse
